From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andrei Aldea <andrei1998@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 23 Jul 2026 12:45:00 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: ti: include BeagleY-AI Armbian supplement

Keep Armbian's board-local USB, PCIe, HDMI, and audio wiring in a directly
managed device-tree include. The upstream-maintained board DTS remains
intact and only needs this stable include point.

Signed-off-by: Andrei Aldea <andrei1998@gmail.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/ti/k3-am67a-beagley-ai.dts | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/ti/k3-am67a-beagley-ai.dts b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/ti/k3-am67a-beagley-ai.dts
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/ti/k3-am67a-beagley-ai.dts
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/ti/k3-am67a-beagley-ai.dts
@@ -401 +401,2 @@ &sdhci1 {
 #include "k3-j722s-ti-ipc-firmware.dtsi"
+#include "k3-am67a-beagley-ai-armbian.dtsi"
